{"tid":2207563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英、李柱銘等15人涉未經批准集結 將分四案審理","createTime":"2020-09-18T09:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T11:12:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f85e7ca28aeaea277a64a6d2c0244fe58c439a20","tid":2207563,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:00:47.000Z","msg":"警方大舉拘捕包括壹傳媒創辦人黎智英、民主黨創黨主席李柱銘等泛民15人，控告他們去年反修例運動期間組織及煽惑參與未經批准遊行等罪，涉及4次遊行。案件今於區域法院提堂，但由於涉及人數眾多，案件移師西九龍裁判法院處理。除早前表明認罪的區諾軒外，餘下被告皆表明不認罪。由於辯方將涉案《公安條例》第17A條的合憲性提出挑戰，控方欲先處理有關法律爭議再作審訊，以便節省法庭和被告時間，但辯方反對。法官高勁修坦言，控方基於被告利益而提出合併申請，實在奇怪；最終接納辯方陳詞，將四案分開並由同一法官負責審理。<br />\n<br />\n案件今移師西九龍裁判法院處理，梁耀宗、吳文遠、梁國雄及蔡耀昌今表明不認罪，換言之，除區諾軒外，餘下涉及四宗案件的14名被告，皆表明不認罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/S7EQRH3X6ZFUBAM7TGSQE7KBMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FS7EQRH3X6ZFUBAM7TGSQE7KBMQ%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAda0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=e3149e92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FS7EQRH3X6ZFUBAM7TGSQE7KBMQ%2F&h=74f0e782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/S7EQRH3X6ZFUBAM7TGSQE7KBMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"39cbf583d285ff71c797a9301e839941fc272494","tid":2207563,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c00021830d223f5d11020a5017bcdef61380e0","tid":2207563,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39cbf583d285ff71c797a9301e839941fc272494","tid":2207563,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"